the user enters information into an HTML form on a page, and upon
submitting the page the data is collected and emailed to an address of
the administrator's choosing.
</p>
          <p>Form-to-Mail (FTM) is designed with reuse, and
hopefully some security, in mind. Email addresses such as sender and
recipient are configured by the administrator, stored in the database,
